This trendy looking pouch set is a must have for every working individual carry your daily lunch in this one and pamper yourself with fresh food daily. These air tight containers helps you to store a larger quantity of food and keep it healthy and fresh. With its amazing quality of being freezer resistant the food can be stored for a long time. These containers feature a four-sided interlocking system and can be stacked from top to bottom or sideways to save space in refrigerator or on counterparts

Features
  • Set of 4

  • 1 piece - Round Glass Container - 500 ml
  • 1 piece - Thermal Pouch to carry 4 containers

  • Clear Glass Look

Care Tips
